Harkonnens%2C%20and%20what%20does%20that%20tell%20us%20about%20the%20sisterhood%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22olivia%20williams%20and%20emily%20watson%20as%20tula%20and%20valya%20harkonnen%2C%20in%20middle%20age.%20they're%20in%20a%20stone%20room%2C%20both%20wearing%20long%20black%20dresses%20with%20their%20hair%20tied%20back.%20tula%20is%20sitting%20on%20a%20chair%20looking%20up%20at%20valya%2C%20who%20stands%20above%20her%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6758c19edc8b666017f2688b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOlivia%20Williams%20and%20Emily%20Watson%20as%20Tula%20and%20Valya%20Harkonnen%20in%20%26quot%3BDune%3A%20Prophecy.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EAttila%20Szvacsek%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20really%20fun%20to%20have%20this%20familial%20sisterhood%20between%20Valya%20Harkonnen%20and%20Tula%20Harkonnen%20at%20the%20center%20of%20a%20larger%20sisterhood%20with%20all%20the%20women%20at%20the%20school.%20That%20baked-in%20choice%20I%20thought%20was%20so%20strong%2C%20and%20the%20premise%20unfolded%20from%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETelling%20the%20sisters'%20story%20requires%20two%20different%20timelines%20in%20the%20show%2C%20with%20younger%20and%20older%20versions%20of%20both%20Valya%20and%20Tula.%20How%20did%20you%20manage%20that%2C%20and%20craft%20the%20throughline%20of%20their%20relationship%20in%20both%20eras%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20like%20we're%20all%20a%20product%20of%20our%20past%20selves%2C%20and%20our%20history%20over%20time.%20The%20Bene%20Gesserit%20and%20the%20sisterhood%2C%20at%20this%20time%20period%2C%20they're%20big%20on%20long-term%20plans%2C%20and%20eventually%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20put%20into%20motion%20a%20plan%20that%20would%20last%20many%20thousands%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20it%20begins%20when%20Valya%20Harkonnen%20comes%20into%20contro