It's%20incredibly%20rewarding.%20First%20of%20all%2C%20I%20think%20we%20have%20to%20start%20with%20%26quot%3BDune%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20women%20are%20players%20in%20such%20a%20pivotal%20and%20real%20way.%20Right%20in%20the%20narrative%2C%20you're%20brought%20on%20board%20as%20an%20equal%20in%20terms%20of%20who's%20pulling%20the%20strings%2C%20and%20the%20Imperium.%20That's%20just%20exciting.%20As%20a%20creator%2C%20of%20course%20I%20want%20my%20women%20characters%20to%20be%20having%20an%20impact%20on%20story%20as%20much%20as%20anyone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20yes%2C%20there's%20nothing%20better%20than%20feeling%20all%20your%20characters%20have%20a%20specificity%20and%20a%20voice.%20It%20was%20really%20fun%20to%20center%20the%20Bene%20Gesserit%2C%20and%20the%20sisterhood%2C%20and%20the%20Harkonnen%20sisters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it's%20certainly%20not%20out%20to%20be%20a%20treatise%20on%20gender.%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20discussions%20with%20the%20Herbert%20estate.%20Just%20that%20idea%20that%20he's%20always%20thinking%20about%20how%20social%20structures%20and%20social%20forces%20might%20change%2C%20but%20be%20familiar%20even%20while%20utterly%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BDune%3A%20Prophecy%26quot%3B%20airs%20on%20Sundays%20at%209%20p.m.%20ET%20on%20HBO%20and%20streams%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dfed657e5d456898628c785351016f7b12b4d269a5d17af0f15435159aef229d0%26postID%3D675378713f5709140470b17a%26postSlug%3Ddune-prophecy-showrunner-alison-schapker-interview-2024-12%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.max.com%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMax%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdune-prophecy-showrunner-alison-schapker-interview-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2F