ing%20Hussain%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Birreplaceable%20legend%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20of%20music%20will%20be%20lesser%20without%20tabla%20maestro%20Ustad%20Zakir%20Hussain.%20Heartfelt%20condolences%20to%20his%20family%2C%20friends%20and%20his%20fans%20all%20around%20the%20world.%20My%20prayers%2C%20Om%20Shanti%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFilmmaker%20Hansal%20Mehta%20credited%20Hussain%20for%20bringing%20%26quot%3Ban%20accompanying%20instrument%20to%20the%20forefront%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20maestro%2C%20Ustad%20Zakir%20Hussain%20passed%20away%20a%20few%20hours%20ago.%20Goodbye%20Ustad%20ji.%20The%20man%20who%20made%20the%20tabla%20sexy%2C%20who%20brought%20an%20accompanying%20instrument%20to%20the%20forefront%20is%20gone.%20Deepest%20condolences%20to%20his%20family%2C%20fans%20and%20students%20around%20the%20globe%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mehta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20called%20the%20percussionist%20%26quot%3Ba%20beacon%20of%20India's%20rich%20musical%20heritage%20and%20a%20true%20custodian%20of%20classical%20traditions%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUstad%20Zakir%20Hussain%20was%20instrumental%20in%20popularising%20Indian%20music%20across%20the%20globe%2C%20serving%20as%20a%20beacon%20of%20India's%20rich%20musical%20heritage.%20A%20true%20custodian%20of%20classical%20traditions%2C%20his%20contributions%20to%20the%20arts%20remain%20unparalleled.%20His%20passing%20is%20a%20monumental%20loss%20to%20culture%20and%20humanity.%20Heartfelt%20condolences%20to%20his%20loved%20ones%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Vijayan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20his%20condolences%20to%20Hussain's%20family%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20called%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bcultural%20ambassador%20who%20bridged%20borders%20and%20generations%20with%20his%20mesmerising%20rhythms%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Padma%20Vibhushan%20t