le%20option%20compared%20to%20water-intensive%20cotton%2C%20explains%20Major%20Tanay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20company%20produces%20handicrafts%20and%20packaging%20materials%20using%20banana%20fibre.%20With%20the%20goal%20of%20establishing%20banana%20fibre%20as%20a%20signature%20product%20of%20Nagaland%2C%20it%20has%20trained%20700%20artisans%20across%20Nagaland%20and%20other%20Northeast%20Indian%20states%20to%20create%20handmade%20items%20from%20the%20fibre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fho_0vUAs4-w%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20founder%2C%20Nengneithem%20Hengna%2C%20who%20brings%2013%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20handicrafts%20sector%2C%20began%20working%20with%20banana%20fibre%20in%202019.%20She%20experimented%20with%20different%20grades%20of%20fibre%2C%20braiding%20techniques%2C%20and%20stitching%20methods.%20She%20met%20Major%20Maben%20during%20COVID%20relief%20efforts%2C%20and%20they%20discovered%20shared%20goals.%20This%20collaboration%20led%20to%20the%20official%20incorporation%20of%20the%20company%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBanana%20is%20a%20zero-waste%20cash%20crop%20which%20yields%20a%20variety%20of%20products%20and%20by-products%20within%20a%20year%20of%20planting.%20It%20grows%20well%20in%20gently%20sloping%20terrain%20and%20is%20low-maintenance.%20Also%2C%20banana%20fibre%20is%20a%20very%20versatile%20fibre%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Major%20Tanay.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20coarser%20type%20can%20be%20used%20to%20make%20coasters%20while%20the%20delicate%20variety%20can%20be%20used%20to%20craft