C%20bags%2C%20clutches%2C%20coasters%2C%20table%20mats%2C%20wall%20hangings%2C%20lanterns%20and%20baskets.%20The%20prices%20of%20these%20products%20range%20from%20Rs%20300%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%2C%20says%20Nengneithem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-8_11zon-1733816737.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Products%20made%20using%20banana%20fibre.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-8_11zon-1733816737.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-8_11zon-1733816737-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-8_11zon-1733816737-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-8_11zon-1733816737-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-8_11zon-1733816737-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388050%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EProducts%20made%20using%20banana%20fibre%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Hengna%20%26amp%3B%20Maben%20Private%20Limited%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20two%20units%20in%20Dimapur%20and%20Athibung%2C%20employing%20over%2030%20artisans.%20We%20provide%20banana%20fibre%20and%20bark%20as%20eco-friendly%20fillers%20for%20packaging.%20We%20also%20use%20these%20materials%20to%20package%20our%20own%20handicrafts%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20product%20is%20delivered%2C%20customers%20can%20repurpose%20the%20fibre%20from%20the%20packaging%20in%20their%20gardens%2C%20as%20it%20provides%20valua