%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337729%2Fbihar-bamboo-startup-entrepreneur-satyam-sundaram-eco-friendly-products-profits%2F%5C%22%3Eeco-friendly%20bamboo%3C%2Fa%3E%20composite%20boats%2C%20offering%20sustainable%20water%20mobility%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20innovation%20took%20over%20two%20years%20to%20materialise.%20Our%20boats%20are%20made%20of%2085%20percent%20bamboo%2C%2010%20percent%20polymers%2C%20and%20five%20percent%20fibre-glass.%20The%20main%20advantage%20of%20bamboo%20composite%20boats%20is%20their%20sustainability.%20Bamboo%20is%20six%20times%20more%20sustainable%20than%20hardwood%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20fast-growing%2C%20abundant%2C%20and%20incredibly%20strong%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ravi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20glimpse%20into%20the%20boat-making%20process%20(L)%2C%20Ravi%20J%20Deka%20(R)%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-11-1733819460-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388086%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20glimpse%20into%20the%20boat-making%20process%20(L)%2C%20Ravi%20J%20Deka%20(R)%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Akvotr