%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20XI%20team%20set%20a%20target%20of%20251%20runs%20in%20front%20of%20Chairman%2011%20team%20after%20losing%207%20wickets%20in%2020%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20the%20Chairman%2011%20team%20could%20score%20only%20178%20runs%20after%20losing%208%20wickets%2C%20in%20which%20former%20cricketer%20Mohammad%20Azharuddin%20scored%20the%20highest%2074%20runs%20facing%2042%20balls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnurag%20Thakur%20was%20awarded%20the%20Man%20of%20the%20Match%20for%20his%20performance.%20The%20best%C2%A0bowler%20was%20Deepender%20Hooda%2C%20best%20fielder%20Nishikant%20Dubey%2C%20best%20batsman%20Mohammad%20Azharuddin%2C%20golden%20duck%20jointly%20by%20Ram%20Mohan%20Naidu%20and%20Imran%20Pratapgarhi%2C%20super%20six%20by%20K.%20Sudhakar%2C%20super%20catch%20by%20Manoj%20Tiwari%2C%20maximum%20boundaries%20by%20Anurag%20Thakur%2C%20fighter%20of%20the%20match%20title%20was%20given%20to%20Chandrashekhar%20Azad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Birla%2C%20who%20arrived%20to%20inaugurate%20this%20match%20congratulated%20the%20MPs%20for%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20awareness%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Parliament%20of%20India%20represents%20140%20crore%20people%20and%20expects%20that%20the%20society%20should%20benefit%20from%20the%20experience%20of%20the%20public%20representatives.%20We%20have%20to%20make%20India%20TB%20free%20by%202025%20and%20this%20friendly%20match%20of%20MPs%20will%20work%20to%20spread%20awareness%20about%20TB%20eradication.%20I%20congratulate%20all%20the%20MPs%20participating%20in%20this%20match%20and%20the%20organiser%20of%20this%20program%20Anurag%20Singh%20Thakur%20ji%20that%20they%20have%20made%20a%20meaningful%20effort%20towards%20eradicating%20a%20disease%20like%20TB.%20If%20we%20all%20work%20with%20full%20determination%20to%20spread%20awareness%20about%20TB%20elimination%20in%20our%20respective%20areas%2C%20then%20we%20will%20definitely%20be%20successful%20in%20eradicating%20TB%20from%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPiyush%20Goyal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFirst%20of%20all%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20congratulate%20Anurag%20Thakur%20ji%2C%20the%20organiser%20of%20this%20wonderful%20and%20successful%20program%2C%20who%20won%20everyone's%20heart%20with%20his%20batting%20today%20and%20who%20brought%20so%20many%20MPs%20on%20one%20platform%20to%20spread%20awareness.%20Anurag%20ji%20had%20given%20a%20message%20against%20TB%20by%20organising%20a%20similar%20match%20in%202018%20and%20after%20today's%20match%2C%20I%20am%20hopeful%20that%20his%20resolution%20will%20go%20across%20the%20country%20and%20such%20matches%20will%20be%20organised%20in%20many%20other%20cities%20as%20well.%20I%20am%20sure%20that%20such%20events%20will%20give%20more%20strength%20to%20the%20resolution%20of%20the%20Hon'ble%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20make%20India%20TB%20free%20by%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thakur%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20ji%20has%20set%20a%20target%20of%20making%20India%20TB%20free%20by%202025.%20And%20to%20spread%20awareness%20towards%20achieving%20this%20target%2C%20selected%20MPs%20from%20all%20parties%20of%20the%20Indian%20Parliament%20participated%20in%20this%20friendly%20cricket%20match%20named%20TB%20Free%20India%20Awareness%20Cricket%20Match.%20Awareness%20about%20TB%20should%20reach%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20country.%20To%20promote%20this%20cause%2C%20we%20have%20united%20with%20team%20spirit%2C%20without%20any%20politics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20endeavour%20is%20that%20such%20events%20should%20continue%20to%20be%20held%20in%20the%20future%20and%20the%20state%20governments%20of%20various%20states%20should%20also%20come%20forward%20to%20spread%20awareness%20against%20TB%20through%20such%20events.%20The%20target%20of%20eradicating%20TB%20worldwide%20is%202031.%20If%20you%20see%2C%20from%202015%20till%20now%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%2038%20percent%20decline%20in%20TB-related%20deaths%20in%20India.%20There%20is%20an%20approximate%2018%20percent%20decline%20in%20new%20cases.%20It%20has%20decreased%20by%20approximately%208%20percent%20worldwide.%20This%20means%20India%20is%20doing%20better%20than%20the%20world.%20Today%2C%20there%20is%20a%20treatment%20for%20it%20and%20the%20government%20also%20provides%20free%20medicines.%20It%20also%20gives%20Rs%201%2C000%20for%20nutrition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734319020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F7ok92v6o_anurag-thakur_625x300_16_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanurag-thakur-hits-ton-as-lok-sabha-speaker-xi-beat-rajya-sabha-chairman-xi-in-charity-match-7257670%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20match%20played%20to%20spread%20awareness%20towards%20'TB%20Free%20India'%2C%20Anurag%20Thakur%20captained%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20XI%20while%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20led%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Chairman%20XI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanurag-thakur-hits-ton-as-lok-sabha-speaker-xi-beat-rajya-sabha-chairman-xi-in-charity-match-7257670%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bitcoin%20surges%20to%20record%20high%20above%20%24106%2C000%20on%20strategic%20reserve%20hopes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734318667000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcryptocurrency%2Fbitcoin-surges-to-record-high-above-106-000-on-strategic-reserve-hopes-124121600113_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bitcoin%2C%20the%20world's%20biggest%20and%20best%20known%20cryptocurrency%2C%20hit%20a%20high%20of%20%24106%2C533%20and%20last%20tr