%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20intent%20is%20to%20bring%20the%20house%20back%20to%20its%20former%20glory%20with%20one%20or%20two%20modern%20touches%2C%26quot%3B%20Jason%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20they%20were%20prepared%20for%20the%20challenges%20of%20fixing%20up%20the%20old%20house%2C%20they%20were%20surprised%20by%20the%20amount%20of%20wildlife%20they%20encountered%2C%20including%20both%20spiders%20and%20snakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20we've%20got%20monkeys%2C%20we've%20got%20centipedes%2C%20we've%20got%20bears%2C%20and%20killer%20hornets%20too.%20I%20was%20chased%20by%20one%20inside%20the%20house%2C%20so%20that%20was%20really%20scary%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20it%20makes%20a%20funny%20story%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Deborah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20language%20barrier%20was%20also%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20challenge%20for%20Jason%2C%20even%20though%20he's%20taking%20Japanese%20classes%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20really%20speak%20Japanese%2C%20whereas%20Deb%20can.%20So%20it%20puts%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20on%20her%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20Jason%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20being%20in%20Tokyo%20or%20Kyoto%20where%20a%20lot%20of%20Japanese%20speak%20English.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221317%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchen%20after%20restoration.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6757f74fdc8b666017f23995%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22988%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20splits%20their%20time%20between%20Australia%20and%20Japan.%3Cp%3ENekoAshi%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20expects%20to%20spend%20the%20next%20few%20years%20chipping%20away%20at%20this%20project.%20They%20have%20also%20started%20documenting%20their%20restoration%20progress%20on%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40NekoAshiJapan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20got%20no%20urgent%20timeframe%2C%20and%20we're%20not%20trying%20to%20make%20money%20out%20of%20the%20property.%20We%20don't%20want%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-turned-japanese-farmhouse-into-mountainside-airbnb-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAirbnb%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20or%20anything%20like%20that.%20This%20is%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Deborah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20still%20lives%20primarily%20in%20Brisbane%2C%20where%20their%20jobs%20are%20based.%20They%20plan%20to%20continue%20splitting%20their%20time%20between%20Japan%20and%20Australia%20until%20they%20fully%20retire%20in%20%26quot%3Bhopefully%20five%20to%20eight%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Deborah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ad9ffb7f-1707-4d59-80cd-6b3eb184f61f%5C%22%3EIntegrating%20into%20the%20local%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20they're%20back%20in%20Australia%2C%20the%20akiya%20sits%20empty%2C%20but%20Jason%20said%20they've%20installed%20cameras%20around%20the%20property%20so%20they%20can%20monitor%20the%20yard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20has%20also%20become%20friends%20with%20the%20real-estate%20agent%20who%20handled%20their%20akiya%20transaction%20%E2%80%94%20so%20much%20so%20that%20he%20even%20drives%20by%20their%20property%20once%20a%20week%20just%20to%20check%20on%20it%20on%20their%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20front%20of%20the%20akiya%20during%20spring.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6757f73e91c1cc343d47931f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20say%20it%20is%20their%20responsibility%20as%20akiya%20owners%20to%20be%20heavily%20involved%20in%20the%20local%20community.%3Cp%3ENekoAshi%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBuilding%20relationships%20with%20their%20neighbors%20and%20the%20wider%20community%20has%20been%20the%20key%20to%20the%20success%20of%20their%20akiya%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20got%20a%20good%20support%20network%20there%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20just%20come%20along.%20You've%20got%20to%20work%20at%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Deborah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20they've%20been%20involved%20in%20the%20local%20community%20since%20day%20one%2C%20and%20even%20joined%20the%20neighborhood%20association.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20couple%20says%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-moved-japan-bought-ski-house-foreigner-renovation-community-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparticipating%20in%20the%20local%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20aspects%20of%20buying%20an%20akiya%20in%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20standing%20on%20a%20grassy%20river%20bank.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675136fb8fbb2783ed2fd780%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22788%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20September%2C%20they%20traveled%20from%20Australia%20to%20Japan%20to%20join%20their%20neighbors%20in%20cleaning%20up%20the%20local%20river.%3Cp%3ENekoAshi%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20why%20the%20local%20akiya%20bank%20was%20so%20invested%20in%20knowing%20why%20the%20couple%20wanted%20to%20buy%20the%20property%2C%20Jason%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeople-moving-buying-abandoned-homes-japan-let-foreigners-own-home-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eforeigners%20have%20been%20snapping%20up%20these%20old%2C%20abandoned%20homes%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20part%20due%20to%20the%20low%20price%20tags%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20restrictions%20on%20foreigners%20purchasing%20property%20in%20Japan.%20For%20many%20of%20them%2C%20it's%20more%20affordable%20to%20own%20an%20akiya%20in%20Japan%20than%20to%20own%20real%20estate%20in%20their%20home%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20most%20cases%20potential%20buyers%20are%20asked%20their%20intentions%20before%20attending%20a%20viewing%20or%20submitting%20an%20application%2C%26quot%3B%20Alex%20Shapiro%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.blackshiprealty.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlackship%20Realty%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Tokyo-based%20real-estate%20agency%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20local%20municipal%20governments%20may%20prioritize%20potential%20buyers%20who%20intend%20to%20live%20there%2C%20contribute%20to%20the%20local%20community%2C%20and%20pay%20local%20government%20taxes%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20each%20local%20government%20sets%20its%20own%20rules%2C%20Sami%20Senoussi%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fakiyaheaven.jp%2F%23about%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAkiya%20Heaven%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20offers%20consulting%20services%20for%20akiya%20purchases%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20rural%20communities%2C%20especially%20those%20with%20aging%20populations%2C%20impose%20stricter%20guidelines%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20preserve%20the%20character%20and%20culture%20of%20their%20towns%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20In%20more%20urban%20areas%2C%20including%20Tokyo%2C%20it's%20less%20common%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20potential%20buyers%20may%20also%20be%20asked%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20they%20have%20the%20financial%20capacity%20to%20fund%20the%20renovations%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20akiya%20in%20question%20requires%20significant%20repairs%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20while%20buying%20an%20akiya%20may%20be%20relatively%20affordable%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20fixing%20the%20house%20up%20can%20balloon%20quickly%2C%20Jason%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20time%2C%20effort%2C%20and%20money%20that%20needs%20to%20go%20into%20them.%20And%20commitment%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can't%20just%20turn%20up%20in%20the%20community%20and%20play%20no%20part.%20You've%20got%20to%20put%20an%20equal%20amount%20of%20time%20into%20the%20house%20as%20much%20as%20you've%20got%20to%20put%20it%20into%20the%20community%2C%20and%20forge%20those%20relationships%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20recently%20relocated%20to%20a%20new%20country%20and%20found%20your%20dream%20home%3F%20If%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%2C%20contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aagoh%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eagoh%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-x-couple-bought-abandoned-house-japan-akiya-restoration-retirement-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734308041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6757beafdc8b666017f23812%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-x-couple-bought-abandoned-house-japan-akiya-restoration-retirement-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20couple%20was%20told%20that%20the%20house%20in%20Japan%20had%20been%20vacant%20for%2012%20years%20and%20had%20served%20as%20a%20sake%20brewery%20until%20the%20early%201900s.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22agoh%40businessinsider.com%20(Amanda%20Goh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A198%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-x-couple-bought-abandoned-house-japan-akiya-restoration-retirement-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20a%20nation%20of%201.45%20billion%20wants%20more%20children%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734307832000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fich