he%20has%20not%20passed%20away.%20We%20ask%20for%20prayers%20for%20my%20Uncle's%20health.%20Can%20you%20please%20remove%20this%20misinformation.%20He%20is%20in%20a%20serious%20condition%20and%20we%20ask%20for%20all%20his%20fans%20around%20the%20world%20to%20pray%20for%20his%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ameer%20Aulia%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bombay-born%20eldest%20son%20of%20legendary%20tabla%20player%20Allah%20Rakha%2C%20Zakir%20Hussain%20followed%20in%20the%20footsteps%20of%20his%20father%2C%20becoming%20a%20marquee%20name%20in%20India%20and%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BZakir%20Hussain%2C%20the%20peerless%20North%20Indian%20tabla%20player%2C%20favors%20an%20impish%20strain%20of%20virtuosity.%20He's%20a%20fearsome%20technician%20but%20also%20a%20whimsical%20inventor%2C%20devoted%20to%20exuberant%20play.%20So%20he%20rarely%20seems%20overbearing%2C%20even%20when%20the%20blur%20of%20his%20fingers%20rivals%20the%20beat%20of%20a%20hummingbird's%20wings%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20New%20York%20Times%20about%20the%20artist%20when%20he%20performed%20at%20Carnegie%20Hall%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20narrating%20the%20story%20of%20his%20first%20booking%2C%20the%20percussionist%20said%20a%20letter%20came%20to%20their%20house%20offering%20a%20concert%20date%20to%20his%20father.%20Zakir%20wrote%20back%20saying%20that%20his%20father%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20accept%20the%20engagement%20but%20that%20his%20son%20was%20available.%20However%2C%20he%20didn't%20mention%20in%20the%20letter%20that%20he%20was%20only%2013.%20It%20worked%2C%20and%20his%20musical%20career%20was%20under%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20musician%20has%20worked%20with%20several%20renowned%20international%20and%20Indian%20artistes%2C%20but%20it%20was%20his%201973%20musical%20project%20with%20English%20guitarist%20John%20McLaughlin%2C%20violinist%20L%20Shankar%2C%20and%20percussionist%20TH%20'Vikku'%20Vinayakram%20that%20brought%20together%20Indian%20classical%20