3Cli%3EIsak%20Andic%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20fashion%20brand%20Mango%2C%20has%20died%20in%20an%20accident%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAndic%20fell%20into%20a%20ravine%20while%20hiking%20in%20caves%20near%20Barcelona%2C%20according%20to%20reports.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAndic%20and%20his%20family%20have%20an%20estimated%20net%20worth%20of%20%244.5%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20Forbes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIsak%20Andic%2C%20the%20billionaire%20founder%20of%20the%20European%20fashion%20company%20Mango%2C%20died%20on%20Saturday.%20He%20was%2071.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndic%2C%20who%20served%20as%20the%20company's%20non-executive%20chairman%2C%20died%20after%20an%20accident%2C%20Mango%20CEO%20Toni%20Ruiz%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsak%20has%20been%20an%20example%20for%20all%20of%20us.%20He%20dedicated%20his%20life%20to%20Mango%2C%20leaving%20an%20indelible%20mark%20thanks%20to%20his%20strategic%20vision%2C%20his%20inspiring%20leadership%20and%20his%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20values%20that%20he%20himself%20imbued%20in%20our%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Ruiz%20said%20in%20the%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERuiz%20praised%20Andic's%20%26quot%3Bcare%20and%20affection%20that%20he%20always%20had%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPedro%20S%C3%A1nchez%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20Spain%2C%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20that%20Andic%20died%20in%20an%20accident%20in%20the%20caves%20of%20Salnitre%20in%20Collbat%C3%B3%2C%20which%20is%20just%20outside%20of%20Barcelona.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20multiple%20reports%2C%20Andic%20fell%20into%20a%20ravine%20while%20hiking%20through%20caves%20with%20his%20family.%20The%20ravine%20was%20over%20320%20feet%20deep%2C%20CNN%20reported%2C%20citing%20local%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20Mango's%20website%20featured%20a%20tribute%20to%20Andic%20on%20its%20home%20page%2C%20and%20photos%20show%20the%20flags%20at%20the%20company's%20headquarters%20in%20Barcelona%20flying%20at%20half-mast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndic%20started%20the%20company%20in%20Barcelona%20in%201984.%20According%20to%20Mango's%20website%2C%20it's%20now%20in%20over%20120%20markets%20and%20has%20a%20thriving%20online%20presence.%20Forbes%20reported%20that%20Andic%20and%20his%20family%20are%20worth%20%244.5%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisak-andic-billionaire-founder-fashion-mango-death-barcelona-cave-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734287566000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675f1e89ec3fba82bfa93b3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisak-andic-billionaire-founder-fashion-mango-death-barcelona-cave-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Isak%20Andic%2C%20the%20billionaire%20founder%20of%20the%20fashion%20brand%20Mango%2C%20died%20in%20an%20accident.%20He%20fell%20while%20hiking%20through%20caves%20near%20Barcelona%2C%20reports%20say.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kbalevic%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Balevic)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A370%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisak-andic-billionaire-founder-fashion-mango-death-barcelona-cave-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22D%20Fadnavis%20Says%20%26quot%3BPerformance%20Review%26quot%3B%20Of%20New%20Ministers%20Soon%2C%20Adds%20A%20Warning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2039%20legislators%20from%20Mahayuti%20allies%20were%20sworn%20in%20on%20Sunday%20in%20the%20first%20cabinet%20expansion%20of%20the%2010-day-old%20Devendra%20Fadnavis-led%20ministry%20including%2016%20new%20faces%2C%20while%2010%20former%20ministers%20were%20excluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPortfolios%20will%20be%20allocated%20in%20the%20next%20two%20to%20three%20days%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%2033%20legislators%20were%20sworn%20in%20as%20cabinet%20ministers%2C%20six%20took%20oath%20as%20ministers%20of%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20inductees%20will%2C%20however%2C%20have%20to%20perform%20with%20Mahayuti%20allies%20deciding%20to%20conduct%20a%20%26quot%3Bperformance%20audit%26quot%3B%20of%20ministers%20during%20their%20tenure%2C%20Fadnavis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProminent%20leaders%20who%20couldn't%20find%20a%20place%20in%20the%20new%20council%20of%20ministers%20include%20BJP's%20Sudhir%20Mungantiwar%2C%20senior%20NCP%20leader%20Chhagan%20Bhujbal%2C%20and%20Shiv%20Sena's%20Abdul%20Sattar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20council%20of%20ministers%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20old%20and%20new%20faces%20which%20reflects%20Fadnavis'%20efforts%20in%20balancing%20caste%20equations%20including%20sections%20of%20Marathas%2C%20OBCs%2C%20SCs%2C%20and%20STs%20and%20striking%20a%20regional%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20new%20inductees%2C%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20Fadnavis-led%20ministry%20has%20gone%20up%20to%2042%2C%20including%20the%20CM%20and%20his%20deputies%20Eknath%20Shinde%20(Shiv%20Sena)%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%20(NCP).%20One%20berth%20was%20kept%20vacant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20secured%2019%20ministerial%20berths%20by%20virtue%20of%20being%20the%20largest%20among%20allies%2C%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20were%20allotted%2011%20and%209%20berths%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernor%20C%20P%20Radhakrishnan%20administered%20the%20oath%20to%20the%20new%20ministers%20at%20a%20ceremony%20held%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20state%20legislature's%20winter%20session%20in%20Nagpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20after%20the%20cabinet%20was%20expanded%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20winter%20session%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20legislature%2C%20Fadnavis%20said%20Mahayuti%20allies%20have%20agreed%20to%20conduct%20a%20%26quot%3Bperformance%20audit%26quot%3B%20of%20ministers%20during%20their%20tenure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Fadnavis%20didn't%20mention%20any%20timeline%2C%20Deputy%20CM%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20Eknath%20Shinde%20said%20the%20ministers%20of%20his%20party%20will%20get%20two-and-a-half%20years%20and%20those%20who%20perform%20will%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20NCP%20leader%20Ajit%20Pawar%20said%20%26quot%3Bnon-performers%26quot%3B%20can%20be%20replaced%20in%20two-and-a-half%20months%20also.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20before%20the%20cabinet%20expansion%20ceremony%2C%20Pawar%20said%20that%20some%20of%20those%20who%20took%20oath%20would%20have%20a%20tenure%20of%20two-and-a-half-years%2C%20underlining%20constraints%20in%20accommodating%20aspirations%20of%20hopefuls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFadnavis%20said%20the%20Mahayuti%20government%20will%20start%20working%20towards%20developing%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20decided%20on%20the%20portfolio%20allocation%20and%20it%20will%20be%20announced%20in%20two%20to%20three%20days.%20Our%20administration%20will%20focus%20on%20swift%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFadnavis%20said%20he%20and%20his%20deputies-%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar-%20have%20told%20new%20ministers%20that%20they%20would%20be%20subjected%20to%20a%20performance%20audit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPerformance%20audit%20of%20ministers%20will%20be%20done%20and%20all%20three%20of%20us%20have%20agreed%20to%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CM%20said%20those%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJP%20who%20couldn't%20find%20a%20place%20in%20the%20Cabinet%20may%20be%20assigned%20an%20organisational%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShinde%20said%20he%20had%20decided%20at%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20party%20level%20to%20give%20two-and-a-half%20years%20to%20new%20ministers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20work%20good%20will%20progress%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20won%20the%20maximum%20132%20seats%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%2C%20got%20the%20largest%20chunk%20of%2016%20ministers%20of%20Cabinet%20rank%20and%20three%20MoS.%20Shiv%20Sena%20was%20allotted%20nine%20positions%20as%20Cabinet%20ministers%20and%20two%20MoS%2C%20while%20the%20NCP%20will%20have%20eight%20ministers%20of%20Cabinet%20rank%20and%20a%20minister%20of%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20new%20inductees%2C%20four%20are%20women%2C%20including%20Pankaja%20Munde%2C%20Madhuri%20Misal%2C%20and%20Meghna%20Bordikar%20of%20BJP%20and%20Aditi%20Tatkare%20of%20NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMunde%20and%20Tatkare%20took%20oath%20as%20Cabinet%20ministers%2C%20and%20Bordikar%20and%20Misal%20as%20MoS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProminent%20leaders%20excluded%20in%20the%20new%20Cabinet%20are%20Bhujbal%20and%20Dilip%20Walse%20Patil%20of%20NCP%2C%20and%20Mungantiwar%20and%20Vijaykumar%20Gavit%20of%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20former%20ministers%20Tanaji%20Sawant%2C%20Deepak%20Kesarkar%2C%20and%20Abdul%20Sattar%20were%20not%20re-inducted.%20Anil%20Patil%2C%20Sanjay%20Bandsode%2C%20and%20Dharmarao%20Baba%20Atram%20of%20NCP%20also%20missed%20the%20second%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20at%20Raj%20Bhavan%20in%20Nagpur%20was%20conducted%2033%20years%20after%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20Sudhakarrao%20Naik%20cabinet%20in%201991.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Cabinet%20expansion%20saw%20the%20re-entry%20of%20state%20BJP%20chief%20Chandrashekhar%20Bawankule%2C%20Jaykumar%20Raval%2C%20Pankaja%20Munde%2C%20and%20Ashok%20Uike%20who%20had%20served%20as%20ministers%20during%20Fadnavis'%20first%20term%20from%202014%20to%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegion-wise%2C%20a%20maximum%20of%20nine%20ministers%20are%20from%20the%20western%20Maharashtra%20region%2C%20followed%20by%20eight%20ministers%20from%20north%20Maharashtra%2C%20seven%20from%20Vidarbha%2C%20six%20from%20Marathwada%2C%20four%20from%20the%20Mumbai%2FThane%20region%2C%20and%20five%20from%20the%20coastal%20Konkan%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20presser%2C%20Fadnavis%20slammed%20the%20opposition%20MVA%20for%20terming%20the%20Mahayuti%20government%20a%20%26quot%3Bgovernment%20of%20EVM%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20government%20came%20to%20power%20because%20every%20vote%20has%20gone%20for%20Maharashtra.%20My%20government%20works%20by%20the%20Constitution%20and%20respecting%20the%20dignity%20of%20the%20Constitution%20is%20our%20priority%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFadnavis%20announced%20an%20SIT%20probe%20into%20the%20murder%20of%20Massajog%20village%20sarpanch%20Santosh%20Deshmukh%20in%20Beed%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20case%20has%20been%20given%20to%20CID%20and%20an%20SIT%20will%20be%20set%20up.%20Culprits%20will%20be%20punished%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20violence%20in%20Parbhani%20was%20orchestrated%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20stone%20replica%20of%20the%20Constitution%20was%20desecrated%20by%20a%20mentally%20unstable%20person%20who%20has%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CM%20said%20those%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJP%20who%20couldn't%20find%20a%20place%20in%20the%20Cabinet%20may%20be%20assigned%20an%20organisational%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFadnavis%20said%20the%20Mahayuti%20government%20was%20ready%20to%20respond%20to%20all%20issues%20raised%20by%20the%20Opposition%20provided%20they%20do%20so%20in%20the%20legislature%20instead%20of%20speaking%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734286980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F8r860t1o_devendra-fadnavis-ani_625x300_06_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fd-fadnavis-sa