%20control'%20of%20AI%20drones%20in%20warfare%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eric%20Schmidt%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675dfb2027808b3289cd4394%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222198%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20Google%20CEO%20and%20White%20Stork%20defense%20startup%20founder%20Eric%20Schmidt%20say%20AI%20drones%20are%20the%20future%20of%20war.%3Cp%3EShahar%20Azran%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFormer%20Google%20CEO%20Eric%20Schmidt%20says%20human-directed%20AI-controlled%20drones%20are%20the%20future%20of%20war.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESchmidt's%20startup%2C%20White%20Stork%2C%20is%20developing%20drones%20for%20Ukraine%20to%20use%20in%20its%20war%20with%20Russia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20drones%20are%20a%20growing%20trend%20in%20military%20innovation%2C%20as%20is%20tech%20to%20counter%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20Google%20CEO%20Eric%20Schmidt%20says%20AI%20drones%20are%20the%20future%20of%20warfare%20but%20that%20human%20operators%20will%20need%20to%20ensure%20they%20don't%20go%20haywire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchmidt%20was%20Google's%20CEO%20from%202001%20to%202011.%20He%20is%20now%20the%20founder%20of%20an%20AI%20drone%20startup%20called%20White%20Stork%2C%20which%20has%20provided%20Ukraine%20with%20drones%20to%20use%20in%20its%20war%20with%20Russia.%20At%20a%20Stanford%20lecture%20in%20August%2C%20Schmidt%20said%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feric-schmidt-white-stork-ai-drones-ukraine-war-russia-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewar%20in%20Ukraine%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20turned%20him%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Blicensed%20arms%20dealer.%26quot%3B%20Schmidt%20said%20at%20the%20Stanford%20lecture%20that%20the%20startup's%20goal%20is%20to%20use%20AI%20%26quot%3Bin%20complicated%2C%20powerful%20ways.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchmidt's%20White%20Stork%20and%20Palmer%20Luckey's%20Anduril%20are%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-military-weapons-tech-startups-anduril-white-stork-shield-ai-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeveloping%20autonomous%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20US%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchmidt%20has%20said%20he%20imagines%20a%20future%20where%20humans%20are%20far%20from%20the%20front%20line%20of%20conflicts%2C%20operating%20from%20afar%20machines%20that%20do%20the%20actual%20fighting.%20Speaking%20to%20PBS%20on%20Friday%2C%20Schmidt%20said%20that%20using%20armed%20men%20on%20the%20battlefield%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bantiquated%20method%20of%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20correct%20model%2C%20and%20obviously%20war%20is%20horrific%2C%20is%20to%20have%20the%20people%20well%20behind%20and%20have%20the%20weapons%20well%20up%20front%2C%20and%20have%20them%20networked%20and%20controlled%20by%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmidt%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20future%20of%20war%20is%20AI%2C%20networked%20drones%20of%20many%20different%20kinds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20tech%20conference%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20in%20October%2C%20Schmidt%20called%20tanks%20%26quot%3Buseless%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20a%20%245%2C000%20drone%20could%20destroy%20a%20%245%20million%20American%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchmidt%20said%20it's%20more%20important%20that%20the%20United%20States%20maintains%20the%20%26quot%3Bhuman%20in%20the%20loop%26quot%3B%20rule%20for%20AI%20drones%2C%20meaning%20that%20a%20person%20will%20have%20%26quot%3Bmeaningful%20human%20control%26quot%3B%20of%20drones%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20will%20happen%20is%20that%20the%20computer%20will%20produce%20the%20battle%20plan%20and%20the%20human%20will%20authorize%20it%2C%20thereby%20giving%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20both%20authorizing%20it%20as%20a%20human%20but%20also%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20control%20and%20liability%20if%20they%20make%20a%20mistake%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmidt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20human%20operator%20is%20key%20to%20preventing%20a%20%26quot%3BDr.%20Strangelove%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmidt%20said%2C%20where%20%26quot%3Byou%20have%20an%20automatic%20weapon%20which%20makes%20the%20decision%20on%20its%20own.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20would%20be%20terrible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScott%20Sacknoff%2C%20president%20of%20aerospace%20and%20defense%20investment%20firm%20Spade%20Index%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanduril-palmer-luckey-trump-streamline-military-contracts-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20autonomous%20drones%20in%20warfare%20are%20%26quot%3Bdefinitely%20a%20trend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%2020%20years%2C%20the%20defense%20sector%20sort%20of%20goes%20through%20a%20cycle%20where%20here%20are%20the%20new%20technologies%20that%20will%20have%20a%20greater%20impact%20on%20defense%20and%20military%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESacknoff%20said%20the%20military%20defense%20business%20is%20always%20looking%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bcounter%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20newest%20technology%20and%20that%20the%20growth%20of%20autonomous%20drones%20would%20likely%20bring%20more%20innovations%20to%20stop%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feric-schmidt-google-white-stork-future-war-ai-networked-drones-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734280618000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675dfc2227808b3289cd43a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feric-schmidt-google-white-stork-future-war-ai-networked-drones-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Google%20CEO%20Eric%20Schmidt%20said%20AI%20powered%20drones%20are%20the%20future%20of%20warfare%2C%20but%20th