caption%3EVermont%20Republican%20Gov.%20Phil%20Scott%2C%20right%2C%20easily%20won%20reelection%20even%20as%20voters%20in%20his%20state%20overwhelmingly%20backed%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20for%20president.%3Cp%3ESuzanne%20Kreiter%2FThe%20Boston%20Globe%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EVermont%2C%20home%20to%20Sen.%20Bernie%20Sanders%2C%20has%20long%20been%20known%20for%20its%20progressive%20politics.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20in%20the%20November%20general%20election%2C%20Republicans%20made%20key%20inroads%20in%20state%20legislative%20races.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMany%20voters%2C%20who%20generally%20back%20Democrats%20on%20the%20federal%20level%2C%20sided%20with%20the%20GOP%20on%20local%20issues.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20decades%2C%20Vermont%20has%20become%20known%20for%20its%20progressive%20politics%2C%20with%20figures%20like%20independent%20Sen.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbernie-sanders-warning-labels-ultra-processed-foods-maha-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBernie%20Sanders%3C%2Fa%3E%20dominating%20the%20New%20England%20state's%20political%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20federal%20level%2C%20the%20Democratic%20edge%20is%20clear.%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20defeated%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20by%20over%2031%20points%20in%20Vermont%2C%20one%20of%20her%20top%20showings%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20popular%20Republican%20governor%2C%20Phil%20Scott%2C%20even%20voted%20for%20Harris%2C%20declaring%20he%20%26quot%3Bput%20country%20over%20party.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20further%20down-ballot%2C%20Republicans%20made%20some%20key%20gains%20in%20Vermont%2C%20breaking%20Democratic%20supermajorities%20as%20voters%20concerned%20about%20affordability%20boosted%20the%20GOP%20in%20a%20series%20of%20pivotal%20races.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20November%20general%20election%2C%20Democrats%20held%20107%20out%20of