Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDion%20McNeeley%20in%20front%20of%20the%20fourth%20investment%20property%20he%20acquired.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dion%20McNeeley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETo%20find%20deals%2C%20Dion%20McNeeley%20focuses%20on%20how%20many%20days%20a%20property%20has%20been%20on%20the%20market.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20investor%20targets%20properties%20that%20have%20been%20listed%20for%20at%20least%20three%20times%20the%20average.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20'days%20on%20market'%20strategy%20helped%20him%20negotiate%20a%20seller%20down%20by%20%24100%2C000.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReal-estate%20investor%20Dion%20McNeeley%20used%20to%20prioritize%20speed%20when%20making%20an%20offer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%2010%20years%20of%20investing%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20fast.%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20an%20offer%20in%20within%20a%20day%20or%20two%20of%20a%20property%20hitting%20the%20MLS%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20veteran%20investor%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20multiple%20listing%20service.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-prepare-for-recession-real-estate-investor-early-retirement-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%2016-unit%20portfolio%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20generates%20enough%20cash%20flow%20to%20more%20than%20cover%20his%20lifestyle%2C%20McNeeley%20is%20less%20focused%20on%20acquiring%20properties%20quickly%20and%20more%20concerned%20with%20finding%20the%20best%20deal.%20To%20do%20so%2C%20he's%20paying%20attention%20to%20one%20specific%20metric%3A%20the%20number%20of%20days%20a%20property%20has%20been%20on%20the%20market.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGenerally%20speaking%2C%20the%20longer%20a%20home%20has%20been%20on%20the%20market%2C%20the%20more%20motivated%20the%20seller%20will%20be.%20%26quot%3BLong%26quot%3B%20is%20relative%20to%20the%20average%20time%20a%20home%20sits%20on%20the%20market%2C%20which%20varies%20by%20location.%20In%20some%20areas%2C%20the%20average%20could%20be%2010%3B%20in%20others%2C%20it%20could%20be%2030.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMcNeeley%2C%20who%20studies%20his%20market%20in%20Tacoma%2C%20Washington%20by%20looking%20at%20listings%20daily%2C%20knows%20that%20the%20average%20home%20sits%20for%20six%20to%20nine%20days%2C%20at%20least%20in%20December%20of%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20rule%20of%20thumb%20is%20to%20take%20the%20average%20and%20triple%20it.%20That's%20the%20number%20you're%20looking%20for%20when%20looking%20at%20listings.%20In%20his%20case%2C%20he%20rounded%20up%20the%20average%20to%2010%20and%20is%20looking%20specifically%20for%20homes%20that%20have%20been%20listed%20for%20at%20least%2030%20days.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20he%20comes%20across%20a%20property%20he%20likes%20that%20meets%20his%20days-on-market%20criteria%2C%20he%20makes%20an%20offer%20that%20will%20get%20him%20the%20return%20he's%20looking%20for.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investor-explains-live-in-brrrr-strategy-save-taxes-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elatest%20property%20he%20purchased%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%94%3Cspan%3E%20a%20duplex%20that%20needed%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20done%20%E2%80%94%20had%20been%20on%20the%20market%20for%20over%20100%20days.%20It%20was%20listed%20for%20%24500%2C000%2C%20but%20based%20on%20the%20renovations%20McNeeley%20would%20need%20to%20complete%2C%20he%20calculated%20that%20the%20deal%20would%20only%20work%20if%20he%20could%20buy%20it%20for%20significantly%20less.%20BI%20verified%20all%20of%20his%20property%20ownership%20claims.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20offered%20400%2C000%20because%20that's%20the%20number%20that%20made%20sense%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20McNeeley%20said.%20His%20offer%20initiated%20a%20two-month%20negotiation.%20%26quot%3BI%20never%20moved%20from%20400.%20It%20went%20from%20500%20to%20477%20to%20444%20to%20422.%20When%20I%20got%20another%20offer%20accepted%20somewhere%20else%2C%20I%20contacted%20them%20to%20say%20I%20was%20pulling%20my%20offer.%20They%20said%2C%20'We'll%20take%20your%20400.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you're%20going%20after%20a%20home%20that's%20been%20on%20the%20market%20for%20longer%20than%20average%2C%20there%20may%20be%20something%20wrong%20with%20it%2C%20and%20it's%20important%20to%20do%20your%20due%20diligence.%20Or%2C%20it%20could%20simply%20be%20listed%20poorly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20the%20agent%20was%20lazy%20and%20took%20bad%20pictures%20or%20doesn't%20have%20it%20listed%20correctly%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20McNeeley.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20case%2C%20it%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20both%3A%20The%20property%2C%20which%20he%20purchased%20in%20July%202023%2C%20ended%20up%20needing%20%2462%2C000%20worth%20of%20renovations%2C%20which%20he%20was%20prepared%20for%2C%20and%20it%20wasn't%20what%20it%20appeared%20on%20the%20listing.%20It%20was%20listed%20as%20a%20single-family%20home%20but%20was%20actually%20a%20duplex%2C%20which%20he%20found%20out%20by%20calling%20the%20gas%20and%20utility%20companies%20and%20asking%20how%20many%20meters%20there%20were.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt%20had%20two%20meters%20for%20electric%20and%20two%20meters%20for%20gas.%20Everything%20about%20this%20was%20duplex%2C%20but%20the%20picture%20looked%20like%20a%20house%2C%20and%20the%20realtor%20listed%20it%20as%20a%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETalking%20to%20the%20gas%20company%2C%20he%20learned%20that%20the%20gas%20hadn't%20been%20paid%20in%20months%20and%20had%20been%20shut%20off%2C%20further%20indicating%20that%20he%20could%20be%20working%20with%20a%20motivated%20seller.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20when%20I%20offered%20400%2C000%2C%20I%20didn't%20raise%20the%20number%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20figuring%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20seller%20has%20to%20sell%2C%20they'll%20take%20my%20number.%20If%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20sell%2C%20they'll%20just%20leave%20it%20listed%2C%20or%20they'll%20take%20it%20down%20and%20not%20sell.%20So%2C%20you're%20not%20always%20guaranteed%20to%20get%20a%20low%20offer%20accepted.%20Sometimes%20people%20don't%20have%20to%20sell%20%E2%80%94%20they%20are%20just%20willing%20to%20for%20a%20higher%20amount.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investor-shares-his-top-strategy-for-finding-deals-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734275281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675c9dafcf8d1359a2e0018d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investor-shares-his-top-strategy-for-finding-deals-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThe%20longer%20something%20sits%20on%20the%20MLS%2C%20the%20lower%20the%20offer%20you%20can%20make.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investor-shares-his-top-strategy-for-finding-deals-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20kicked%20out%20from%20Path%20of%20Exile%202%20for%20'cheating'%20weeks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734274889000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116341238%2Cimgsize-30768.cms%22%2C%22originI