%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E's%20inauguration.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAmazon%2C%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20and%20Meta%20are%20each%20prepared%20to%20donate%20%241%20million.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere%20are%20virtually%20no%20limits%20on%20inaugural%20donations%2C%20meaning%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20can%20cut%20massive%20checks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBig%20Tech%20companies%20and%20the%20moguls%20behind%20them%20are%20preparing%20to%20make%20six-figure%20donations%20to%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump's%20inaugural%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-life-career-education%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJeff%20Bezos'%20Amazon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20and%20Mark%20Zuckerberg's%20Meta%20have%20all%20been%20reported%20to%20have%20made%20or%20will%20make%20%241%20million%20to%20the%20outfit%20tasked%20with%20planning%20and%20organizing%20Trump's%20triumphant%20return%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20financing%20of%20inaugurations%20is%20really%20a%20cesspool%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20campaign%20financing%2C%26quot%3B%20Craig%20Holman%2C%20a%20lobbyist%20for%20government%20watchdog%20Public%20Citizen%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHolman%20said%20there%20are%20few%2C%20if%20any%2C%20limits%20to%20inaugural%20donations%2C%20and%20what%20makes%20them%20particularly%20appealing%20is%20that%20megadonors%20and%20CEOs%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20picking%20the%20loser.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnlike%20financing%20a%20campaign%2C%20when%20you%20don't%20know%20for%20sure%20who%20is%20going%20to%20win%2C%20here%20in%20the%20inauguration%2C%20you've%20got%20the%20winner%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20corporations%20and%20other%20special%20interests%20just%20throw%20money%20at%20them%20at%20the%20feet%20of%20the%20president%20with%20the%20hope%20of%20currying%20favor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeff%20Hauser%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Revolving%20Door%20Project%2C%20a%20public%20interest%20group%2C%20said%20donations%20to%20the%20inaugural%20committee%20are%20less%20likely%20to%20irk%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20frequently%20a%20mechanism%20for%20entities%20that%20sit%20out%20elections%20to%20get%20good%20with%20the%20incoming%20administration%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%202017%20inaugural%20set%20a%20record%2C%20raking%20in%20roughly%20%24107%20million.%20Las%20Vegas%20Sands%20CEO%20Sheldon%20Adelson%20donated%20%245%20million%2C%20the%20largest%20single%20donation.%20AT%26amp%3BT%20gave%20just%20over%20%242%20million.%20For%20many%20in%20Washington%2C%20it%20was%20a%20time%20to%20make%20nice%20with%20an%20incoming%20president%20that%20few%20thought%20would%20win%20the%202016%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20Trump's%20inaugural%20offers%20one%20final%20major%20opportunity%20for%20CEOs%20to%20curry%20influence%20with%20the%20president-elect%20at%20his%20peak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20he'll%20be%20term-limited%2C%20the%20next%20major%20fundraising%20opportunity%20likely%20won't%20come%20until%20Trump%20begins%20preparations%20for%20a%20presidential%20library%20(should%20that%20even%20occur).%20At%20that%20point%2C%20companies%20will%20have%20missed%20their%20window%20to%20make%20a%20final%20impression%20before%20mergers%20and%20acquisitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222de3580a-843a-4565-9d02-53e9adba7ef6%5C%22%3E2017%20Trump%20inaugural%20donors%20benefited%20greatly%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPlaying%20ball%20can%20have%20major%20benefits.%20OpenSecrets%20found%20in%202018%20that%20%26quot%3Bof%20the%2063%20federal%20contractors%20that%20donated%20to%20the%20inauguration%2C%20more%20than%20half%20won%20multimillion-dollar%20bids%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20federal%20government%20later%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EForeign%20donors%20can't%20contribute%20to%20a%20president-elect's%20inaugural%20committee%2C%20and%20the%20committee%20must%20publicly%20disclose%20details%20about%20donations%20over%20%24200%20within%2090%20days%20of%20Inauguration%20Day.%20Otherwise%2C%20there%20are%20few%20limits%20on%20what%20individuals%20or%20corporations%20can%20give%2C%20and%20inaugural%20committees%20are%20not%20required%20to%20explain%20how%20they%20spend%20the%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20presidents%2C%20especially%20Obama%20in%202009%2C%20have%20imposed%20voluntary%20restrictions%20on%20donations.%20Obama%20refused%20to%20accept%20corporate%20donations%20or%20individual%20contributions%20over%20%2450%2C000%20for%20his%20historic%20first%20inauguration%2C%20though%20he%20later%20lifted%20those%20limits%20for%20his%20reelection%20celebration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHauser%20said%20donations%20will%20allow%20corporations%20to%20prepare%20for%20an%20especially%20transactional%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20corporations%20with%20an%20agenda%20in%20Trump's%20Washington%2C%20be%20it%20offense%2C%20like%20getting%20new%20contracts%2C%20or%20defense%2C%20like%20avoiding%20negative%20federal%20scrutiny%2C%20are%20going%20to%20spend%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20Washington%20to%20either%20make%20or%20protect%20billions%20in%20the%20real%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Hauser%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22366115a7-890d-4c5f-ad21-17a9c8a85cd3%5C%22%3ETech%20companies%20are%20under%20the%20microscope.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20all%20faced%20antitrust%20concerns.%20Republican%20lawmakers%20have%20frequently%20grilled%20Meta%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20Facebook's%20decision%20to%20limit%20sharing%20the%20New%20York%20Post's%20initial%20report%20on%20Hunter%20Biden's%20laptop%20ahead