ijo-das-journey-to-becoming-ultraviolette-photographer%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Protect%20Your%20Indoor%20Plants%20From%20the%20Winter%20Chill%20With%20These%208%20Tips%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWinter%20can%20be%20a%20tough%20time%20for%20indoor%20plants.%20The%20combination%20of%20colder%20temperatures%2C%20reduced%20sunlight%2C%20and%20fluctuating%20humidity%20levels%20can%20stress%20even%20the%20hardiest%20of%20houseplants.%20But%20with%20a%20little%20extra%20care%2C%20you%20can%20keep%20your%20green%20companions%20thriving%20all%20winter%20long.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20a%20guide%20to%20help%20you%20protect%20and%20nurture%20your%20plants%20during%20this%20chilly%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Adjust%20the%20watering%20schedule%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20winter%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F382844%2Fgrow-avocado-indoors-guide-small-space-home-gardening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20indoor%20plants%20%3C%2Fa%3Egenerally%20need%20less%20water%20because%20their%20growth%20slows%20down.%20The%20cooler%20temperatures%20and%20reduced%20sunlight%20also%20mean%20that%20the%20soil%20takes%20longer%20to%20dry%20out%2C%20increasing%20the%20risk%20of%20overwatering.%20Overwatered%20plants%20are%20more%20prone%20to%20root%20rot%20and%20fungal%20infections%2C%20which%20can%20damage%20the%20plant%20permanently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20avoid%20overwatering%2C%20check%20the%20moisture%20level%20of%20the%20soil%20before%20watering.%20Stick%20your%20finger%20about%20an%20inch%20into%20the%20soil%20%E2%80%94%20if%20it%20feels%20dry%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20time%20to%20water.%20If%20it%20still%20feels%20moist%2C%20wait%20a%20few%20more%20days%20before%20checking%20again.%20For%20plants%20like%20succulents%20or%20cacti%2C%20which%20are%20more%20drought-tolerant%2C%20water%20even