ndia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhoney-business-1-1733829777-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388198%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJagpal%20says%20he%20has%20trained%20at%20least%20500%20farmers%20in%20beekeeping.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2059%2C%20Jagpal%20actively%20shares%20his%20knowledge%20and%20experience%20with%20other%20farmers%2C%20demonstrating%20the%20practical%20application%20of%20beekeeping%20techniques.%20By%20mentoring%20and%20guiding%20others%2C%20he%20ensures%20that%20the%20benefits%20of%20beekeeping%20are%20accessible%20and%20sustainable%20in%20the%20long%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20he%20has%20trained%20at%20least%20500%20farmers%20in%20beekeeping.%20One%20such%20farmer%20is%20Dharmaveer%20Singh%20Nandal%20from%20Mehrana%20village%20in%20Jhajjar%20district.%20With%20Jagpal%E2%80%99s%20guidance%2C%20Dharmaveer%20learned%20about%20beekeeping%20and%20soon%20set%20up%20his%20own%20business%20in%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20with%2030%20bee%20boxes%2C%20and%20now%20I%20have%202%2C500%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dharmaveer%20Singh%20Nandal%20from%20Mehrana%20village.%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20I%20was%20a%20bit%20sceptical%20and%20scared%20about%20handling%20honey%20bees.%20But%20Jagpal%3Cem%3E%20ji%3C%2Fem%3E%20helped%20me%20understand%20the%20nature%20of%20bees%20and%20the%20advantages%20of%20beekeeping.%20Compared%20to%20farming%20wheat%2C%20paddy%2C%20and%20mustard%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20very%20beneficial.%20Today%2C%20I%20earn%20between%20Rs%205%20to%2010%20lakh%20a%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20been%2025%20years%20since%20Jagpal%20started%20in%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F147834%2Fnews-maharashtra-lady-beekeeper%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20honey%20business%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Reflecting%20on%20his%20decision%2C%2